As someone who isn't a sports fan in the very least.. I Felt the loss of that very special extraordinary man.
I live in LA.. And it would be impossible not to know what he meant to our city. Like Jimmy said, He was ours. And to lose him was already such a tragic and unfair loss, but then to find out his daughter went with him is unfathomable.
I think it's great that Jimmy had no audience and devoted his entire time slot to remember this amazing man. Rest in peace you two..
Even in death Kobe & Gigi are inspiring people to love more. They're journey is not over.
